"title": "5836: disgrace",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5836: disgrace",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Shame and dishonour that can arise from sin and idolatry. The exile of Israel brought disgrace upon God's name. God's people may suffer disgrace for the sake of Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>Examples of disgrace</h2>\n<h3>Brought on Israel</h3>\n<p>As the result of Achan stealing what was dedicated to God:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:1-Josh7:5\">JOS 7:1–7:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:11-Josh7:15\">JOS 7:11–7:15</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:23-1Sam17:26\">1SA 17:23–17:26</a> <em>as the result of Goliath's boasting</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps44:9-Ps44:19\">PSA 44:9–44:19</a> <em>when God no longer acted on Israel's behalf</em></p>\n<h3>Brought on Israel's enemies</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:10\">PSA 6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:4\">PSA 35:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:26\">PSA 35:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:14\">PSA 40:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps44:15\">PSA 44:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps70:2\">PSA 70:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:13\">PSA 71:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps83:17-Ps83:18\">PSA 83:17–83:18</a></p>\n<h2>Sin brings disgrace</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:8-Gen3:10\">GEN 3:8–3:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps52:1\">PSA 52:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:5\">PRO 13:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:35\">PRO 14:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:3\">PRO 18:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:25\">JER 3:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:7-Dan9:8\">DAN 9:7–9:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos4:7\">HOS 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:23-Rom2:24\">ROM 2:23–2:24</a></p>\n<h3>False prophets disgraced</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:38-Jer23:40\">JER 23:38–23:40</a></p>\n<h3>Idolaters disgraced</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:16\">ISA 45:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:25\">EXO 32:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:29\">ISA 1:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:26-Jer2:28\">JER 2:26–2:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:6\">HOS 10:6</a></p>\n<h3>The sexually immoral disgraced</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:32-Prov6:33\">PRO 6:32–6:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen34:1-Gen34:7\">GEN 34:1–34:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:17\">LEV 20:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:21\">DEU 22:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg19:22-Judg19:24\">JDG 19:22–19:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg20:4-Judg20:7\">JDG 20:4–20:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:2-2Sam11:5\">2SA 11:2–11:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:14\">2SA 12:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:12-2Sam13:14\">2SA 13:12–13:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:22\">2SA 13:22</a></p>\n<h2>Barrenness could bring disgrace</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:22-Gen30:23\">GEN 30:22–30:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:6\">1SA 1:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:25\">LUK 1:25</a></p>\n<h2>The exile brought disgrace upon God's name</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:20-Ezek36:21\">EZK 36:20–36:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:3\">NEH 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:17\">NEH 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:22\">JER 22:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:51\">JER 51:51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam5:1-Lam5:2\">LAM 5:1–5:2</a></p>\n<h2>God's people may suffer disgrace for the sake of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:26\">HEB 11:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:11-Matt5:12\">MAT 5:11–5:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:22-Luke6:23\">LUK 6:22–6:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:41\">ACT 5:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:13\">HEB 13:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:21\">1PE 2:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:1\">1PE 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:13\">1PE 4:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:10\">1PE 5:10</a></p>",
